		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://example.com/?p=96</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h1><strong>Add the forwarding</strong></h1>
<blockquote>netsh interface portproxy add v4tov4 listenport=&lt;Listen Port&gt; listenaddress=&lt;Listen IP&gt; connectport=&lt;Connect Port&gt; connectaddress=&lt;Connect IP&gt;</blockquote>
<h1>Remove the forwarding</h1>
<blockquote>netsh interface portproxy delete v4tov4 listenport=&lt;Listen Port&gt; listenaddress=&lt;Listen IP&gt;</blockquote>]]></content:encoded>
